&lt;li&gt;Red LED (15mcd, 20mA, Diffused) - LH N974 [Digikey: 475-1416-6-ND]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cree&lt;/b&gt; - Cree High-Power Surface Mount LEDs
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
